metadata.name: FemaleZ_1
metadata.description:
A team of blockchain, art and tech innovators infected by the early dawn of web3. Outlasting the global apocalypse, now united together as The Zombie Social Club. The year is 2022 and ZSC is rapidly infecting the web3 space through a series of zombies themed NFT drops, Metaverse games, Metaverse giveaways, Celebrity Metaverse events/shows, talks, meet and greets and VR based experiences.

The Zombie Social Club’s first outbreak ‘MaleZ’ were 3,000 NFT’s now safely contained by 1,191 holders. Experts advise that on the 29th July a new wave of the ZSC Virus will outbreak and infect 6,000 of the population, resulting in further utility for MaleZ holders, provide breeding opportunities, spawning evil OffspringZ and PetZ to join the MaleZ whilst exploring the Multiverse as their FemaleZ NFT avatars for the ultimate, custom, interactive social and virtual Web3 Metaverse experience.
